('Course Registration forms are now available', 'by Course Rep', 'Course Registration form is now available. See Madam Omoye <a href=\"tel:08163689069\">(08163689069)</a> for original copy. \r\n<p></p>\r\nKindly make a photocopy of the form, fill it with the appropriate details and submit \"individually\" to the MSC Coordinator, Dr. F.I. Amadin <a href=\"tel:07033663388\">(07033663388)</a>. \r\n<p></p>\r\nEducation students are also required to fill the form indicating the 4 courses they are taking.\r\n<p></p>\r\nYour MAT NO. which is one of the required fields on the form -- can be gotten from CRPU, Second Floor, UNIBEN Auditorium.\r\n<p></p>\r\nAlso, the following requirements must be met before the form can be submitted;\r\n<ul class=\"alpha-list\">\r\n<li>Must have completed <a href=\"blog.php?20190204170000\" target=\"_blank\">Physical Clearance</a>.</li>\r\n<li>Must have completed <a href=\"blog.php?20190308170000\" target=\"_blank\">Departmental Clearance</a> and paid the departmental fee of N5,000.</li>\r\n<li>Must have paid school fees of N120,000 for first semester.</li>\r\n<li>Must have contributed for the installation of new chairs in the MSC classroom (N4,500).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\nThe deadline for submission is <b>Tuesday, July 9th, 2019</b>. ', 'reg.png', 'NITDA', 0, '2019-06-25 08:00:00', 58),
('Lecture Note V, CSC839 - Seminar', 'by Dr. S.S. Daodu', 'Rank Correlation.', 'rankcore.png', 'Youtube', 1, '2019-06-25 11:00:00', 59),
('Contribution for repairs of classroom door handle N200', 'by Course Rep', 'Please be informed that all MSC Computer Science students are required to contribute N200 each for repairs of the MSC classroom door handle.\r\n<p></p>\r\nThis was announced by the H.O.D, Dr. S.S. Daodu, on Tuesday, June 25th, 2019. \r\n<p></p>\r\nOur coursemate, Mr Paul will be in school tomorrow by 3pm to fixed the classroom door handle.\r\n<p></p>\r\nKindly make all payments (starting from tomorrow) to the Course Rep, Mr. Tugbeh (<a href=\"tel:08169960927\">08169960927</a>).\r\n\r\n', 'contrib.png', 'Google Search', 0, '2019-06-25 16:00:00', 60),
('Lecture Note VII, CSC841 - Programming Languages', 'by Dr. K.C. Ukaoha', 'Sub-programs.', 'subprog.png', 'Oracle.com', 1, '2019-06-27 11:00:00', 61),
('CSC801 Presentation List', 'by Course Rep', 'The list for CSC801 presentation is outlined below. \r\n<p></p>\r\n<b>NOTE:</b> Any mistakes in the assigned topics stated in this list will be corrected later, kindly continue with the topic you\'re already working on. Also, any name that isn\'t on the list should be reported and will be included today.\r\n<p></p>\r\n<a href=\"media/uploads/downloads/20190628090000.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">[DOWNLOAD] CSC801 Presentation List</a>\r\n<p></p>\r\nIndividuals who want to exchange slots can discuss that within themselves but please do it in a timely manner so as not to delay the duration of the presentation.\r\n<p></p>\r\nIt is currently unclear if powerpoint slides are optional or will attract extra points, but the Asst. Course Rep, Ms. Adeleke (<a href=\"tel:08072104022\">08072104022</a>) will clarify that before the presentation begins. \r\n<p></p>\r\nThe current list for the presentation has a total of 28 students. <b>Presentation begins at 11:00AM</b>. Goodluck to all.\r\n', 'presenter.png', 'Tutsplus.com', 0, '2019-06-28 08:00:00', 62);
